{"tid":5704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[磚]連住尼潮文改篇","createTime":"2016-11-27T04:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T05:27:59.000Z","uid":19285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"acce26bc83eeadb2066a83daad36e5f6cad08bad","tid":5704,"uid":19285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:34:34.000Z","msg":"高登仔已經弱化左<br />\n係時候改返d 潮文更正返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n熄登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』<br />\n連住尼：『Let it go~ left it 高～』"},{"pid":"bfe278d0bc684bbc97f224a593e3124ac56f1a0b","tid":5704,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."},{"pid":"a2e765589b9884d3296f81b1ec774088c8da8c30","tid":5704,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"幽默感既野...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805ecdf5435528901bc8e1fe955c21bac63610cf","tid":5704,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95626f6f289304228af25a8998135ff06cd9e9a3","tid":5704,"uid":10579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-2